message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as the paper deals with speech enhancement and speech intelligibility prediction. Other likely categories could be cs.SI (signal processing), cs.SY (systems and control), cs.LG (machine learning), and cs.CL (computation and language) as the paper involves the use of auditory filterbank and modulation filterbank, and the prediction of speech intelligibility using a new concept based on signal-to-distortion ratio.
